  m_text: 'we ran out of time for a proper introduction, so you get a text explaination
    instead.


    The loop is simple.


    1. Go to the shop above to buy drug
    ingredients.

    2. Go back home and [insert way to make drugs].

    3. Hide
    drugs inside your house until the timer runs out.

    4. Wait for the police
    to search your house.

    5. Repeat until you die =)


    Walking - WASD

    Throwing
    - LMB

    Turning Camera - Q/E


    pretty much it.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 72e14db1bff80b74da07e5aa82fe005f, type: 2}
